=Description=

David Bollier:

"What if a ToS (Terms of Service agreement), instead asserting strict proprietary rights for business purposes, legally authorized and required peer sharing among users of the website?  Such a ToS would assert legal terms for automatic access, use and sharing of collectively “owned” digital resources, perhaps with customizable options for specific needs.  This [[Peer Production ToS]] is now being developed by Intrinsic, [http://www.intrinsic.com] a startup company that is building an open-source architecture for online collaboration."

